	<div class="entry-content">

		<div data-elementor-type="wp-page" data-elementor-id="48771" class="elementor elementor-48771" data-elementor-post-type="page">
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-c975638 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="c975638" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
<div class="e-con-inner">
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a976c43 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="a976c43" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Emeritus Faculty</h2>
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-844d41b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="844d41b" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p><span class="intro">Allen School emeritus faculty are recognized leaders who helped shape our program and our field.</span></p>
</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-783e3aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="783e3aa" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<p>Although retired from full-time research and teaching, many of our emeritus faculty remain actively engaged with our community as we continue to evolve and expand our impact.</p>
</p>
